@host = https://localhost:7288
@hostHttp = http://localhost:5247

### Reference — health check (works out of the box; no upstream call)
GET {{host}}/external/health

### Exercise 1 — list posts from JSONPlaceholder
GET {{host}}/posts

### Exercise 2 — get post by id
GET {{host}}/posts/1
###
GET {{host}}/posts/99999

### Exercise 3 — create a post (forwarded to external API)
POST {{host}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "title": "External request practice",
  "body": "Posted via our proxy endpoint."
}

### Exercise 4 — posts for a user
GET {{host}}/posts/user/1

### Exercise 5 — aggregated summary (post + comment count)
GET {{host}}/posts/1/summary

### Exercise 6 — cancellable list (same route as Exercise 1 once implemented)
GET {{host}}/posts
